author: brane
msg: Do not incompatibly modify SSL cert parsing failures in JavaHL.
Define a bitmask that includes all the failure mode bits.
Check failures parameter against ALL_KNOWN, and do not modify it.
Also check against ALL_KNOWN to determine the result.

msg: QPID-5785: [Java Broker] Fix NPE when a topic exchange is closed after a message filter has been added to an existing binding.
